                    <WebAddress>https://www.supremecourt.gov/publicinfo/year-end/year-endreports.aspx</WebAddress>
                </FooterDetails>
                <Header>Reports on the Federal Judiciary</Header>
                <Paragraph>"Year-End Reports on the Federal Judiciary," which the current and former Chief Justices have prepared, are posted on the Supreme Court's website. Starting with the year 2000, most of the reports are available in Portable Document Format (PDF) for viewing and downloading.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
